5c676f0dd1f09005e78e539daadf3686650f9a","tid":133481,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"巴士好細，冇位你放。<br />\n只可以放坐位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca57cae7b6ae759bc1424347255f42a2620cd3d","tid":133481,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士好細，冇位你放。<br />\n只可以放坐位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指腳前面的位置?"},{"pid":"26f929719db829ba164ca561ff83eeddf568a80c","tid":133481,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"你去浸溫泉定睇個神宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係後者我勸你降低期望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e587aaaa9ec9a98108b516ecf1e54536caa3f68","tid":133481,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去浸溫泉定睇個神宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係後者我勸你降低期望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n浸溫泉，神宮順路望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b750b1f45ae971cbe6b4dee4a293d5c73a47205","tid":133481,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇特別位比你放行李，但冇乜人坐，自己坐埋一邊攬住啲行李啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑假去，希望唔會太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357f3972c0acc5a7ccd71aa6132ba732628702b9","tid":133481,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴士好細，冇位你放。<